OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThe night will then remain largely dry
OL,8,Fwith clear spells. A mild night with
OL,9,Fgentle winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FThe odd spot of rain is
OL,12,Fpossible early morning in the west,
OL,13,Fotherwise dry with plenty of sunshine
OL,14,Fand feeling warm.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FIt
OL,17,Fwill continue to be dry with long
OL,18,Fsunny spells. Feeling very warm but
OL,19,Fbecoming cooler along the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
